						<div class="postbody">Yes, if you do the split during the horizontal blank between lines, there won't be a visible glitch.<br /><br />Most commercial era games failed to do this, perhaps not knowing that it was an option. Crystalis has very notably good splits, I think. In addition to the obvious split for the status bar at the bottom, the field actually splits in the middle of the screen to accommodate a lack of nametable wrapping!<br /><br />Well, at least the field split is in hblank and seamless looking. I guess the status bar has a glitchy line above it. :S</div>

